{"tha-ap374:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap374:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap374:0.3":"Patalipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap374:1.1":"“Vipassi nama bhagava, ","tha-ap374:1.2":"sayambhu aggapuggalo; ","tha-ap374:1.3":"Purakkhato sasissehi, ","tha-ap374:1.4":"pavisi bandhumam jino. ","tha-ap374:2.1":"Tini patalipupphani, ","tha-ap374:2.2":"ucchange thapitani me; ","tha-ap374:2.3":"Sisam nhayitukamova, ","tha-ap374:2.4":"naditittham agacchaham. ","tha-ap374:3.1":"Nikkhamma bandhumatiya, ","tha-ap374:3.2":"addasam lokanayakam; ","tha-ap374:3.3":"Indivaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap374:3.4":"adittamva hutasanam. ","tha-ap374:4.1":"Byagghusabhamva pavaram, ","tha-ap374:4.2":"abhijatamva kesarim; ","tha-ap374:4.3":"Gacchantam samananaggam, ","tha-ap374:4.4":"bhikkhusanghapurakkhatam. ","tha-ap374:5.1":"Tasmim pasanno sugate, ","tha-ap374:5.2":"kilesamaladhovane; ","tha-ap374:5.3":"Gahetva tini pupphani, ","tha-ap374:5.4":"buddhasettham apujayim. ","tha-ap374:6.1":"Ekanavutito kappe, ","tha-ap374:6.2":"yam pupphamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap374:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap374:6.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap374:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap374:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap374:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap374:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma patalipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap374:9.1":"Patalipupphiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}